Date-Discordian version 1.00
============================

A simple, non-OO Discordian date module, and the driver script to
emulate the classic `ddate` cmdline utility.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None

